st", "label": "list"}], "texts": [{"self_ref": "#/texts/0", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "section_header", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 283.652, "t": 225.66729999999995, "r": 1156.335505, "b": 91.00097500000004, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 35]}], "orig": "ELEPHANT       WATCH Camp & Safaris", "text": "ELEPHANT       WATCH Camp & Safaris", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/1", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 207.551, "t": 67.16920000000005, "r": 1232.4493777034002, "b": 29.86329999999998, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 49]}, {"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 773.636, "t": 785.428, "r": 1390.8732320000001, "b": 593.932, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [50, 422]}], "orig": "Explore SENTIENCE in the Wild with Warrior-Nomads Hosted by expert guides from the local community, our unique focus  on  'elephant-watching'  in  Kenya's  exquisite  Samburu reserve introduces guests to the mysterious world of elephant society and sentience. Each newborn calf belongs to a family whose history  we  can  be  trace  back  four  generations  in  this 1000-strong population of individually-known elephants.", "text": "Explore SENTIENCE in the Wild with Warrior-Nomads Hosted by expert guides from the local community, our unique focus  on  'elephant-watching'  in  Kenya's  exquisite  Samburu reserve introduces guests to the mysterious world of elephant society and sentience. Each newborn calf belongs to a family whose history  we  can  be  trace  back  four  generations  in  this 1000-strong population of individually-known elephants."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/2", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 773.636, "t": 554.428, "r": 1390.8724880000002, "b": 362.932, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 383]}], "orig": "Thanks to our partners at  research  NGO  Save  The  Elephants, our  profound  understanding  of  the  bonds  between  cousins and  daughters,  or  late  aunts  and  great  grandmothers  -  that continue to influence relationships between elephant families today - offers fascinating and knowledgeable portraits of these remarkable elephants' lives.  It's a life-changing experience.", "text": "Thanks to our partners at  research  NGO  Save  The  Elephants, our  profound  understanding  of  the  bonds  between  cousins and  daughters,  or  late  aunts  and  great  grandmothers  -  that continue to influence relationships between elephant families today - offers fascinating and knowledgeable portraits of these remarkable elephants' lives.  It's a life-changing experience."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/3", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 773.636, "t": 323.428, "r": 1390.8717200000008, "b": 98.93200000000002, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 397]}], "orig": "These intimate encounters are further enhanced by the insights  of  the  Samburu  people  whose  charm  and  irreverent sense  of  fun  guarantee  an  unforgettable  adventure.  With  a wildlife-tolerant  culture  that  allows  for  peaceful  co-existence with  elephants  and  other  wildlife,  the  nomads  are  crucial stewards of the land and are now emerging as the new faces of conservation.", "text": "These intimate encounters are further enhanced by the insights  of  the  Samburu  people  whose  charm  and  irreverent sense  of  fun  guarantee  an  unforgettable  adventure.  With  a wildlife-tolerant  culture  that  allows  for  peaceful  co-existence with  elephants  and  other  wildlife,  the  nomads  are  crucial stewards of the land and are now emerging as the new faces of conservation."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/4", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": 